{"tid":1241082,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"打擊廢老，由cut CCTVB做起","createTime":"2019-06-18T14:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T16:07:12.000Z","uid":49803,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee21cebf560447ba8cfdc8c1a096cb046ce12a99","tid":1241082,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"屋企兩老太年輕、思想好唔成熟<br />\n睇完CCTVB啲&quot;新聞&quot;再無限上綱<br />\n幾離譜幾難聽嘅嘢我都聽過<br />\n見有巴打用改WIFI密碼訓練兩老唔睇CCTVB<br />\n但我懶得睇實佢地幾時睇，諗住根本做起<br />\ncut電視天線，裝NowTV或CableTV<br />\n<br />\n唔想抽師傅入屋搞，會好大陣仗<br />\n所以諗住整NowE<br />\n有無巴打有跟CSL/1010出NowE？<br />\n是咪所有plan都會包Now新聞台？<br />\n<br />\n如果唔裝NowE，有無乜TV Box可以睇到？<br />\n最好有啲師奶辣殺劇吸引兩老睇<br />\n佢地唔理世事當幫忙都好"},{"pid":"e8377fba04c5a1cff8c88a994ef77213e83c5177","tid":1241082,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d8a00a7d2f468eefb3b4d7bc804bc8729397b7","tid":1241082,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8c40d69413ff35570d7c14426134d660408ee9","tid":1241082,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309d444b8ad8e22b984b50927322a3a88cc0df62","tid":1241082,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35da9f984961550d0acbf6b818b0e4976d73709d","tid":1241082,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb40e84d9f52f2e562b2769c8da438fd89bb6fc3","tid":1241082,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:17:4